
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            -webkit-text-stroke: 1px blue;
        }
        .cat-container{
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        /* .wanttogo {
            position: fixed;
            left: 80px;
            top: 370px;
        } */
        .fullbtn{
            width: -webkit-fill-available;
        }
        .search-res{
            display: none;
            margin-top: 45px;
        }
        .search-normal{
            display: flex;
        }
        .logout-res{
            display: none;
        }
        img{
            height: 300px;
            width: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        iframe{
            width: -webkit-fill-available;
            height: -webkit-fill-available
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .container{
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            .cat-container{
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
            .search-res{
                display: block;
            }
            .search-normal{
                display: none;
            }
            .logout-res{
                display: block;
                position: absolute;
                top: 9px;
                right: 7px;
                z-index: 2000;
            }
        }
    </style>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Destinations</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body>
    <button onclick="location.href = '/logout';" id="logout" class="btn btn-danger ml-3 logout-res">Logout</button>

    <nav class="navbar fixed-top navbar-light justify-content-between" style="background-color: #404243 ;">
        
        <a class="navbar-brand text-white">Rome</a>
        <div class="search-normal">
            <form class="form-inline" method="POST" action='/search'>
            <input name="Search" class="form-control mr-sm-2" type="search" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-success my-2 my-sm-0" type="submit">Search</button>

            </form>
            <button onclick="location.href = '/logout';" id="logout" class="btn btn-danger ml-3">Logout</button>

        </div>    
      </nav>
      
    <br>

    <div class="container search-res">
        <form class="form-inline" method="POST" action='/search'>
            <input name="Search" class="form-control col-md-9" type="search" placeholder="Search" aria-label="Search">
            <button class="btn btn-outline-success my-2 col-md-3" type="submit">Search</button>

        </form>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between">
        <div class="col-md-3 justify-content-center">
            <img id="image" src="/rome.png" style="width: -webkit-fill-available;">
            
            <form method ='post' action ='/add'>
                <br>
                <button type="submit" name="destination" value="rome" id="wanttogo" class="btn btn-secondary ml-3" style="width: -webkit-fill-available;">Add to Want-to-Go List</button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <p>Rome today is one of the most important tourist destinations of the world, due to the incalculable immensity of its archaeological and art treasures, as well as for the charm of its unique traditions, the beauty of its panoramic views, and the majesty of its magnificent villas.</p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>
        <div class="col-md-5" >
            <iframe autoplay
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UDlBySgEJ38">
            </iframe>
        </div>
        <br>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>



